data.description: odern living made easy in this spacious home that is conveniently located near local shopping, schools, and restaurants.The curb appeal is boosted by the welcoming front porch and the stone and brick exterior. The floor plan includes a dining room with bay window, gourmet kitchen and wide open great room with fireplace. Pass down family recipes in the kitchen with white cabinets that perfectly complement the stainless steel appliances and dark granite counters. A high ceiling adds depth to the owner’s suite bedroom and the bathroom has a soaking tub and double sink vanity. Relax on the covered patio that overlooks the huge backyard for those Texas Style BBQ!!
